                      href="/sri-lanka/kandy-sri-lanka/"
                      target="_blank"
                      rel="noreferrer noopener">Kandy</a
                    > to <a
                      href="/sri-lanka/ella-sri-lanka/"
                      target="_blank"
                      rel="noreferrer noopener">Ella</a
                    > should take around 6 hours. However, everything runs a little slower in <a
                      href="/sri-lanka/"
                      target="_blank"
                      rel="noreferrer noopener">Sri Lanka</a
                    >, and there can be longer stops and delays on the journey. In reality, it can take up to 10 hours,
                    but that means more time to see the beautiful views! It might be a long ride, but it’s 100% worth
                    the journey.
