                              target="_blank"
                              rel="noreferrer noopener"
                              data-rich-text-format-boundary="true">Get Kandy Train Tickets here</a
                            >
                          </p>
                        </div>
                      </div><p>
                        If you can, we also recommend avoiding weekends – this is the busiest time, and it can be tough
                        to get a seat. Standing for 9 hours is not fun!
                      </p>
